It was a memorable occasion for all the ladies who attended the 14th Annual Sunflower Fund Ladies Breakfast, in association with Ainsworth Attorneys, which took place at the Coastlands Musgrave Hotel.  The guests looked radiant in their ‘Summer and Sunflowers’ inspired ensembles and enjoyed a morning of meaningful fun, food and pampering in the name of charity and hope. The Sunflower Fund’s vision is “to save the lives of individuals diagnosed with blood diseases by increasing the number of patients making it to transplant”. Funds raised from the event will go toward the fight against blood diseases, like leukaemia, through the recruitment of new blood stem cell donors and the maintenance of a registry of prospective donors who are committed to helping anyone in need of a life-saving stem cell transplant. Seen at the event were: